metadata.name: Metamorphic Album Token #1
metadata.description: You are viewing Metamorphic Album Token #1. Metamorphic Album Token are unique 1/1s representing original ownership of Metamorphic by DAILLY Songs. Metamorphic Album Tokens are tradeable, just like Songs, and grant eventual governance over the public exhibition of Metamorphic. Each Metamorphic Album Token is integrated with a generative Control Strip comprised of a mix of RGB colors, inspired by CRT TV test screens. For more on governance rights and the destroyPublic() function that empowers holders of Album Tokens on-chain visit https://metamorphic.gg and read the FAQ.
